## Issue

I am currently developing a new contract and when I try to migrate the contract I get:

```

"rNFT" -- Invalid number of parameters for "undefined". Got 3 expected 5!.

```

## Steps to Reproduce

Find below my contract. All imports are openzeppelin contracts:

```

pragma solidity >=0.7.0 <0.9.0;

